TEHRAN -- Russian Atomic Energy Minister Yevgeny Adamov arrived here Saturday to inspect the Bushehr nuclear plant which is under construction with Russia 's cooperation .
Upon his arrival , Adamov said that his three-day visit was aimed at reviewing the work carried out in constructing the 1,000-megawatt Bushehr nuclear plant in southern Iran .
